summary: This is an email from an FBI agent to an unknown recipient, transmitting a PDF attachment described as highly confidential responsive material from digital evidence processed by CART. The email indicates the document is being uploaded from FBINET to UNET.
keyFacts: An FBI agent sent an email on January 28, 2021, transmitting confidential material.
The attached PDF contains responsive material from digital evidence processed by CART (Computer Analysis and Response Team).
The document was being transferred from FBINET to UNET, indicating inter-agency or internal sharing of evidence.
